---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Salerno Trucking | Professional Fleet Capacity Solutions"
  description="Professional mixer truck fleet capacity solutions for ready-mix producers and dependable concrete delivery for placement contractors nationwide."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-media"></div>
    <div class="container hero-content reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Family Owned &amp; Operated Since 2009</p>
      <h1>Professional Fleet Capacity Solutions for Ready-Mix Producers</h1>
      <p>Since 2009, Salerno Trucking has partnered with ready-mix producers across the United States to provide dependable mixer truck capacity that helps increase production, protect customer relationships, and keep projects on schedule.</p>
      <div class="button-row">
        <a class="button" href="/partner-with-us">Partner With Us</a>
        <a class="button button-outline" href="/services">Our Services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a class="scroll-cue" href="#family">Scroll</a>
  </section>

  <section id="family" class="section">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Built on Responsibility</p>
        <h2>Family Owned &amp; Operated Since 2009</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="lead">For over 15 years, Salerno Trucking has helped ready-mix producers expand fleet capacity while providing contractors with dependable concrete delivery. We believe every delivery reflects our reputation and the reputation of the partners we serve.</p>
        <div class="values-line">
          <span>Respect</span><span>Integrity</span><span>Stewardship</span><span>Responsibility</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading centered reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Who We Serve</p>
        <h2>Two Sides of the Industry. One Standard of Service.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="service-grid">
        <article class="audience-card producer reveal">
          <div class="card-number">01</div>
          <h3>Ready-Mix Producers</h3>
          <p>Reliable trucks and experienced operators ready to increase fleet capacity, meet peak demand, support growth, and represent your company professionally.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Long-term and seasonal capacity</li>
            <li>Professional representation</li>
            <li>Experienced mixer operators</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="text-link" href="/partner-with-us">Partner With Us →</a>
        </article>
        <article class="audience-card contractor reveal">
          <div class="card-number">02</div>
          <h3>Concrete Placement Contractors</h3>
          <p>Dependable concrete delivery, material sourcing through trusted producers, transparent pricing, and clear communication from scheduling through placement.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>No standing time charges</li>
            <li>Reliable scheduling</li>
            <li>Transparent pricing</li>
          </ul>
          <a class="text-link" href="/partner-with-us">Request Delivery →</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section dark-section">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Raising the Standard</p>
        <h2>The Industry Deserves Better</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <p class="lead">Too often, concrete delivery is undermined by poor communication, unreliable service, and a lack of accountability. Salerno Trucking was built to operate differently.</p>
        <p>We bring professionalism, transparency, and responsibility to every relationship—because our performance reflects both our reputation and yours.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section image-split">
    <div class="image-panel fleet-photo" role="img" aria-label="Concrete mixer truck on a jobsite"></div>
    <div class="content-panel reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">More Than Additional Trucks</p>
      <h2>Fleet Capacity Solutions</h2>
      <p class="lead">We become an extension of your operation.</p>
      <p>Salerno Trucking helps ready-mix producers increase production without compromising service quality. Our experienced operators and dependable equipment integrate into your daily operation to support customer commitments, seasonal demand, and long-term growth.</p>
      <a class="button" href="/services">Explore Producer Services</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Why Salerno Trucking</p>
        <h2>Built to Protect Your Schedule and Your Reputation</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        {['Professional Drivers','Reliable Equipment','Transparent Pricing','Nationwide Experience','Safety','Communication','Integrity','Family Owned'].map((item, i) => (
          <article class="feature-card reveal">
            <span>{String(i + 1).padStart(2,'0')}</span>
            <h3>{item}</h3>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section projects section-muted">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-heading centered reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Featured Projects</p>
        <h2>Experience Across the Concrete Industry</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="project-grid">
        <div class="project-card project-one reveal"><span>Commercial</span></div>
        <div class="project-card project-two reveal"><span>Infrastructure</span></div>
        <div class="project-card project-three reveal"><span>Industrial</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section trust-statement">
    <div class="container narrow reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Trusted Representation</p>
      <h2>Our Partners Don't Just Hire Us.<br />They Trust Us to Represent Their Brand.</h2>
      <p>When a Salerno Trucking mixer truck arrives on a jobsite, it isn't simply delivering concrete.</p>
      <p>It's representing the ready-mix producer who trusted us. It's representing the contractor waiting on schedule. It's representing years of relationships built through professionalism.</p>
      <p>That's why we treat every delivery like it's our own reputation riding down the road.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section promise dark-section">
    <div class="container narrow centered reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Promise</p>
      <h2>Every Delivery Is More Than a Load of Concrete.</h2>
      <p class="lead">It's a reflection of our partners' reputation and our own.</p>
      <p>We promise to represent every ready-mix producer and concrete contractor with professionalism, clear communication, dependable service, and unwavering accountability.</p>
      <p>Whether we're providing additional fleet capacity or delivering concrete to a jobsite, we are committed to protecting schedules, strengthening relationships, and exceeding expectations.</p>
      <p><strong>Because when you partner with Salerno Trucking, your success becomes our responsibility.</strong></p>
      <div class="promise-line">Professionalism Delivered. Partnerships Built.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section partners">
    <div class="container centered reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Trusted By</p>
      <h2>Proudly Supporting Industry Leaders</h2>
      <div class="logo-row">
        <div>PARTNER LOGO</div><div>PARTNER LOGO</div><div>PARTNER LOGO</div><div>PARTNER LOGO</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container centered reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Partner With Salerno Trucking</p>
      <h2>Let's Build Something Strong Together.</h2>
      <a class="button button-light" href="/partner-with-us">Start a Conversation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
